data.description: Built in 1900; this farmhouse will give you the country feels but keep you within a quick drive to the city. Large lot at .66 acres gives you plenty of space. Nice covered front porch to spend your mornings/evenings on and another deck to soak up the sun. At over 2100 sq ft of living space; this 3 bed 2 bath home gives you the ability to bring in your personal touch and make it your own.
